Now, if I see someone selling something for a price that just seems outrageous, I'll let them know privately in tells. Pisses me off when someone shouts that my prices are too high. My prices too high? Then don't fuckin' buy from me.<br>
<br>
But when someone gives out false info on an item, especially when it's info that you can't see on the trade screen, it's perfectly acceptable to correct them publicly.<br>
